snippet.title: Left to Rot - Launch Trailer 4k (Microphone Short Horror Game)
snippet.description:
⚡ - BUY NOW:
🎮 Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2020840/Left_to_Rot/
🎮 Itch.io - https://galacticcrows.itch.io/left-to-rot
⚡ NEW WEBSITE : http://galactic-crows.com ⚡

🎬 JOIN OUR DISCORD: https://discord.gg/qXZUGDvkmV 🎬

Left to Rot is a walking simulator psychological horror game. You take on the role of Luca, a young man caught up in a horrific mystery. If you make noise... It's game over! (You will need a Microphone)!


OUT NOW!
